name: Kolleen Chesley

jv_history.partner_name: ‎Ladies Who Leverage - Kelly Charles-Collins on Apple Podcasts
jv_history.source_quote: is a collaborative, global community of empowered women who leverage their expertise, resources, and relationships to build their business, brand, and badassery. An empowered woman who empowers

what_you_do: Kolleen Chesley empowers women CEOs, founders, and entrepreneurs to streamline operations, drive strategic growth, and uncover hidden revenue opportunities through her organization Powerful Women Synergized.
offering: Community, network of support, and resources for women in business; advocacy for closing the $5–7 trillion power gap for women entrepreneurs.
social_proof: Founder of LeadHERship Global with over 10,000 members internationally; Founding Director of Powerful Women (originally Women's Business Lunch).
business_focus: Empowering women entrepreneurs through community, strategic operations support, and revenue growth strategies.
service_provided: Community building, business strategy, operations streamlining, revenue growth consulting, professional networking
